<stack-static>
    <statement><div><p>A mechanical arm sweeps through <m>{120}</m>. The outer radius is <m>{56}\,\text{m}</m> and the inner radius is <m>{21}\,\text{m}</m>. Calculate the following areas:</p>

<ol type="a">
    <li>
        <p>The area of the smaller circle formed by the arm. <fillin characters="7" name="ans1"/><m>\,\text{m}^2</m> </p>
          
    </li>
    <li>
        <p>The area of the larger circle formed by the arm. <fillin characters="7" name="ans2"/><m>\,\text{m}^2</m></p>
    </li>
    <li>
        <p>The area of the region swept by the mechanical arm. <fillin characters="7" name="ans3"/><m>\,\text{m}^2</m> </p>
    </li>
</ol>



<p/></div></statement>
    <solution><ol type="a">
    <li>
        <p><alert>Area of the smaller circle (inner radius):</alert></p>
        <p>
        <md>
<mrow>A_{\text{inner}} \amp = \pi r^2</mrow>
<mrow>\amp = \frac{22}{7} \times ({21})^2</mrow>
<mrow>\amp = {1386}\ \text{m}^2</mrow>
</md>
        </p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <p><alert>Area of the larger circle (outer radius):</alert></p>
        <p>
        <md>
<mrow>A_{\text{outer}} \amp = \pi R^2</mrow>
<mrow>\amp = \frac{22}{7} \times ({56})^2</mrow>
<mrow>\amp = {9856}\ \text{m}^2</mrow>
</md>
        </p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <p><alert>Area of the region swept by the mechanical arm:</alert></p>
        <p>
        <md>
<mrow>A_{\text{swept}} \amp = \frac{\theta}{360} \pi (R^2 - r^2)</mrow>
<mrow>\amp = \frac{120}{360} \times \frac{22}{7} \times \left( {56}^2 - {21}^2 \right)</mrow>
<mrow>\amp = {2823}\ \text{m}^2</mrow>
</md>
        </p>
        <p>Alternatively, you can subtract the area of the inner circle from the area of the outer circle the multiply by <m>\frac{{120}}{360}</m>:</p>
        <p>
        <md>
<mrow>A_{\text{swept}} \amp = ({9856} - {1386})\times \frac{{120}}{360}</mrow>
<mrow>\amp = {\frac{8470}{3}}\ \text{m}^2</mrow>
<mrow>\amp ={2823}\ \text{m}^2</mrow>
</md>
        </p>
    </li>
</ol></solution>
    <answer><p><m>1386</m></p></answer>
    <answer><p><m>9856</m></p></answer>
    <answer><p><m>2823</m></p></answer>
</stack-static>